军西班牙语国家（拉丁美洲等），开始新的 VTuber 试镜” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/idol-corporation-announces-expansion-into-espanol-spanish-speaking-countries-new-vtuber-auditions-begin/embed/#?secret=sAFCnqH7qV#?secret=ggVUoq9txx" data-secret="ggVUoq9txx" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.idol-company.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">偶像团体</a></p><cite>官方网站</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="JzbdwDMHCK"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/">偶像公司将 75% 的利润返还给 VTuber</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“偶像公司将 75% 的利润返还给 VTuber” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/embed/#?secret=KLCoJ90gI7#?secret=JzbdwDMHCK" data-secret="JzbdwDMHCK" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/">《偶像》将其 75% 的收入返还给其附属的 VTuber 这次不寻常的公开发布的背景</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 99235</post-id></item><item><title> Hololive Production 日本国内团体VTuber频道订阅总数已突破5000万</title><link/>https:/